---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

---

<MainLayout title="Clint Winter" showFooter={false}>
    <div class="hidden max-w-5xl mx-auto sm:p-4 sm:grid grid-cols-12 sm:gap-8 lg:gap-12 xl:gap-20">
        <aside class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-4">
            <img class="rounded-lg w-full bg-transparent" src="/assets/avatar.jpg" alt="Profile avatar" />

            <div class="pt-8">
                <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-base">
                    <li>
                        <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://github.com/ClintWinter">
                            <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Follow me on</span>
                            Github
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://linkedin.com/in/clint-winter">
                            <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Connect with me on</span>
                            LinkedIn
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://twitter.com/clintwinter13">
                            <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Follow me on</span>
                            Twitter
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="/assets/ClintWinterResume.pdf">
                            <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Read my</span>
                            Resume
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://dev.to/clintwinter">
                            <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Follow me on</span>
                            dev.to
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://www.codementor.io/@clintwinter?refer=badge">
                            <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Get coaching on</span>
                            codementor.io
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <section aria-label="About Me" class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">I'm Clint Winter</h1>
            <!-- <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">I'm a software developer at <a class="font-medium text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400 hover:underline" href="https://givebutter.com/" rel="noreferer noopener">Givebutter</a>. I work with Laravel and React in my daily work. I love learning new programming paradigms and finding ways to incorporate them into my problem-solving toolset.</p> -->
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">I'm a seasoned senior full-stack web developer based in New Jersey. My primary focus is on crafting pragmatic solutions that not only get the job done but do so efficiently and elegantly. I firmly believe that perfection, while admirable, should never stand in the way of delivering exceptional results.</p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">My journey in the world of web development began in October 2015 at CWR Electronics, where I honed my skills in JavaScript, jQuery, Bootstrap, CSS, PHP, and MySQL. From there, I continued to evolve, taking on roles at DirectLync, where I worked extensively with PHP, JavaScript, and MySQL, and finally landing at Givebutter in January 2021, where I currently serve as a senior full-stack developer. Laravel and PHP are my forte, and I'm well-versed in React, Typescript, Svelte, and Tailwind CSS as well.</p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">My approach to development is user-centric. I believe in asking the right questions and understanding the unique needs of each project to create solutions that truly resonate with users. Clean code and effective problem-solving are at the core of my work.</p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Welcome to my corner of the web, where I'll be sharing insights, tips, and projects from my journey in web development.</p>
        </section>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:hidden gap-8 p-4">
        <div>
            <img class="rounded-lg w-full bg-transparent" src="/assets/avatar.jpg" alt="Profile avatar" />
        </div>

        <section aria-label="About Me" class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">I'm Clint Winter</h1>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">I'm a software developer at <a class="font-medium text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400 hover:underline" href="https://givebutter.com/" rel="noreferer noopener">Givebutter</a>. I work with Laravel and React in my daily work. I love learning new programming paradigms and finding ways to incorporate them into my problem-solving toolset.</p>
        </section>

        <div>
            <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-base">
                <li>
                    <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://github.com/ClintWinter">
                        <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Follow me on</span>
                        Github
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://linkedin.com/in/clint-winter">
                        <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Connect with me on</span>
                        LinkedIn
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://twitter.com/clintwinter13">
                        <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Follow me on</span>
                        Twitter
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="/assets/ClintWinterResume.pdf">
                        <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Read my</span>
                        Resume
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://dev.to/clintwinter">
                        <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Follow me on</span>
                        dev.to
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a class="group hover:text-violet-500 font-medium" rel="noopener noreferer" href="https://www.codementor.io/@clintwinter?refer=badge">
                        <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-violet-500 font-normal">Get coaching on</span>
                        codementor.io
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainLayout>

